        <notes>Log4j is a transitive dependency of the SpotBugs plugin (spotbugs configuration).
            Not included in published library JARs.</notes>
        <cpe>cpe:2.3:a:apache:log4j:*:*:*:*:*:*:*:*</cpe>
        <cve>CVE-2026-34478</cve>
    </suppress>
